Short description

This is a restaurant automation program.
With this program, the user can reserve a table in the restaurant in advance.
The user can also order food. From the menu page, he can pre-add it to the cart.
To order food or reserve a place, he must pay in advance. For payment, he must add a payment card to his page.

Only the admin can add a food to the menu.
admin page is generated automatically when the program starts working.

Credentials admin
login- admin@mail.ru
password- admin

Tools used

programing language- java
framework- Spring boot
Spring Security, Spring Data JPA
Thymeleaf
Java Script, JQuery, Ajax
HTML, CSS
Gradle
PostgreSql
